# auto-setup

## Context Profile

Load core workspace policy plus architecture and repository-boundary evidence. Do not load scenarios, canary, signatures, or learnings before their producing step.

## Contract

1. Delegate read-only repository exploration and identify product repos versus a meta workspace.
2. Generate or update `ARCHITECTURE.md` and `.autopus/project/{product,structure,tech,workspace}.md` from evidence.
3. Generate `scenarios.md`, then `canary.md`, in that order; record unavailable deploy signals instead of inventing them.
4. Keep source-of-truth, tracked/generated/runtime paths, nested repos, and QA target commands explicit in `workspace.md`.
5. Verify every required document and report its path. Do not edit installed generated platform surfaces.
